Privacy Policy for Fossa

At Fossa, we are committed to protecting the privacy and confidentiality of our users' personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide while using our app. By using our app, you agree to the terms and conditions of this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect:
   - Personal Information: When you create an account or use our app, we may collect certain personal information such as your name, email address, and demographic information.
   - Health Information: Our app may collect health-related information, including exercise data, nutrition logs, and other health-related metrics that you voluntarily provide.

2. Use of Information:
   - Provide Services: We may use the information we collect to provide and personalize our services, including tracking your progress, offering personalized recommendations, and delivering relevant content.
   - Analytics and Improvements: We may analyze user behavior and app usage to improve our services, enhance user experience, and develop new features and functionality.
   - Communication: We may use your contact information to communicate with you about app updates, new features, promotions, and other relevant information.

3. Data Security:
   - We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect the security of your personal information and prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
   - We use industry-standard encryption protocols to safeguard your data during transmission.

4. Data Retention:
   - We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law.

5. Third-Party Services:
   - Our app may integrate with third-party services, such as fitness trackers or social media platforms. Please review the privacy policies of these third-party services as we are not responsible for their practices.

6. Children's Privacy:
   - Our app is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us to have it removed.

7. Updates to Privacy Policy:
   - We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices. We encourage you to review the Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

8. Contact Us:
   - If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, please contact us at fossacare@gmail.com.

By using our app, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information as described herein.

Last updated: 10-7-2023
